infrastructure, and existing and advanced areas of technology. additions to property and equipment will continue, including new facilities and computer systems for research and development, sales and marketing, support, and administrative staff.
commitments for constructing new buildings were $129 million on june 30, 2004. we have operating leases for most u.s. and international sales and support offices and certain equipment under which we incurred rental expense totaling $318 million,
