compensation awards to offset the impact of the special dividend. the special dividend will be payable on december 2, 2004, to shareholders of record on november 17, 2004, conditioned upon shareholder approval of amendments to the employee stock
plans at the annual meeting of shareholders scheduled to be held november 9, 2004.
